data.name: Mikanko Catfight
data.desc: If you control a "Mikanko" monster: Target 1 face-up monster on the field; equip it with 1 appropriate Equip Spell from your Deck. If an Equip Spell(s) is sent to your GY while this card is in your GY (except during the Damage Step): You can banish this card, then target 1 Equip Spell in your GY; add it to your hand. You can only use each effect of "Mikanko Catfight" once per turn.
